# MongoDB Atlas холболтын string (Atlas → Connect → Drivers)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@<cluster>.mongodb.net/nous?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# JWT нууц түлхүүр — урт, санамсаргүй утга өг (production-д заавал сольж)
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-long-random-string
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# Server port
PORT=4000

# Frontend origin (CORS)
CLIENT_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

# Persistent image storage (production-д шаардлагатай)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=
